    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Use with reference to the various interpretations of this phrase from Horace's Ars Poetica in relation to pictorial arts, literally translated "as is painting so is poetry."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
